definitions.definition: A census-designated place in Tulare County , California , United States .
A small village and civil parish (served by Pixley and District Parish Council) in eastern Herefordshire , England ( OS grid ref SO6638 ) .
A small hamlet in Hinstock parish, Shropshire , England ( OS grid ref SJ6826 ) .
